# MongoDB Data Layer

- Use **MongoDB** as the database — never SQL-based databases
- In .NET, use the official `MongoDB.Driver` package
- Define POCO models with `[BsonId]` and `[BsonElement]` attributes
- Use `IMongoCollection<T>` for data access in repository classes
- Store configuration (connection string, database name) in `appsettings.json`
- In the frontend, interact with data only through the .NET API — no direct DB access
